=== ANALYTICAL DERIVATION ===

Numerical integrals over [0, pi/2]:
  I_odd  = int log(1 + 1/(4sin^2 u)) du = 1.51166266
  I_even = int log(1 + 1/(4cos^2 u)) du = 1.51166266
  I_odd / I_even = 1.00000000

