=== THE RATIO DIVERGES! ===
The ratio log(F_odd)/log(F_even) is NOT converging to 6.
It's slowly increasing because log(F_odd) grows as m*log(phi)*2
while log(F_even) grows as m*log(5/4)/2.
The asymptotic ratio should be: 2*log(phi) / (log(5/4)/2)
  = 4*log(phi)/log(5/4) = 8.626049

  Corrected asymptotic ratio = 4*log(phi)/log(5/4) - 1 = 7.626049
  Compare with observed: ~6.0

  4*log(phi)/log(5/4) = 8.626049
  4*log(phi)/log(5/4) - 1 = 7.626049


